{
  "stem": "21788.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You were just supposed to leave it there for the government to confiscate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's what they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They confiscated part of your belongs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember my father taking this man with the lists, sitting him down at a table, a bottle of cognac or whiskey next to him, and a glass.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "After the first hour, he didn't know what went into those boxes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The people that packed the suitcases were also sympathetic to our cause.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I might mention at that time-- that at this time, that not everybody was a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were very, very many Germans that were sympathetic towards the Jews, tried to help them in any way they could without endangering their lives too much.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those were some of the people that said, it's OK.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Put it in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Put it in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so consequently, quite a few of the contraband, if that's what you want to call it, went into both the suitcases, the trunks, and the wooden crates.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What we didn't know at that time was that-- I don't know who was in the know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if the-- the people that packed the suitcases knew it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened at that time is that the German government had no intentions whatsoever to let the wooden crates out of the country.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they left our house, were loaded onto the trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were unloaded someplace else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All the trunks were put on the train ahead of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All the wooden crates were put in a warehouse in Hamburg, where I understand consequently, during the war, were bombed and burned.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there never was any intention of letting any of that stuff get out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
